    35	//! - `p50_ms` / `p99_ms` are omitted for recall-only ACs (AC-013b).
    36	//! - `recall` is omitted/null for latency-only ACs (AC-012, AC-019).
    37	//! - A record MUST carry at least one comparable metric (a latency pair or a
    38	//!   recall value), else it is malformed (exit 2).
    39	//! - **Unknown fields are ignored, not rejected** (forward-extensible).
    40	//!
    41	//! ## Exit codes
    42	//!
    43	//! - `0` = no regression flagged (includes all-insufficient-history).
    44	//! - `1` = at least one group flagged a regression.
    45	//! - `2` = data missing / malformed (directory absent, unreadable/invalid
